## Executive Summary

A comprehensive security audit was conducted on the `GravePresale` and `GraveToken` smart contracts for the Grave Protocol platform. The audit covered presale mechanics, token economics, access control, upgradeability, and resistance to common attack vectors. All identified issues have been remediated. The final codebase meets mainnet security standards.

